      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against published FDA generic centrifugal pump experimental measurements. Predicted NIH values fall within 12% of experimental mean across all 5 operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied for all comparisons against predicate device baseline."
