    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are acceptably scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. Discretization error is below the 5% threshold, NIH predictions are within 15% of experimental measurements across all operating points, and the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied for all predicate comparisons. The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility for the COU decision at the specified assurance level. The governing requirement (https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou1-vv40-2018-hemolysis-req) specifies ASME V&V 40-2018 as the applicable credibility framework standard, consistent with the regulatory submission basis.",
